{"tid":996682,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[ECON垃圾求救]Perfect competition點搵equilibrium no. of firms?","createTime":"2019-01-26T13:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T13:30:12.000Z","uid":193084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c104d12095300697cd3f84d052d29c32c9306d47","tid":996682,"uid":193084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T13:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/26/070856_bd790f09e98fe9201d6dab96775d40c5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F26%2F070856_bd790f09e98fe9201d6dab96775d40c5.png&h=7378aa47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我搵到equilibrium of firms係n*=max{a-b-2}，喺唔知道a同b嘅情況之下我要點搵consumer surplus同producer surplus?<br />\n<br />\n如果a=15, b=3, 咁n*就應該係10<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/26/211936_3e495c493eae5cc1b0beba5a27a4f2f0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F26%2F211936_3e495c493eae5cc1b0beba5a27a4f2f0.png&h=606b2d7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但再加多個tax on profits, t=0.5落去條equation會變成點？<br />\n我睇答案話n*一樣係10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nthanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc48dbe5ccb17511caecf69e9c65b52f8ca391ac","tid":996682,"uid":175298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T07:14:05.000Z","msg":"好耐無掂過計數，唔肯定岩唔岩<br />\n<br />\nPS=p*q*-Int (1-0) S dp<br />\n如果係identical firm ，就咁no. of firms * LMC<br />\n咁PS應該係岩岩好都係max{a-b-2,0}<br />\n<br />\nTax果度係咪miss out左啲野？<br />\nSomehow你modify 返個total cost function 再做多次咪係，但點解係實數黎 <br />\n<br />\nBtw, 咩u ug/pg?"},{"pid":"5aad9ba214129e06d8dbf3c8aa57d0ab7b3c92e1","tid":996682,"uid":175298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T07:18:03.000Z","msg":"好小見高登問到呢個lv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 